85614438.text: "For instance, phosphorylation of TSC2 by ERK and RSK downstream of the growth factor responsive Ras-Raf-MEK pathway inhibits the TSC complex and leads to Rheb and mTORC1 activation, while phosphorylation of TSC2 by AMPK and GSK3 in response to energy stress (e.g. due to limiting levels of glucose) spurs the TSC complex to inhibit Rheb and mTORC1 [XREF_BIBR]."
